&gt; Friends, 
&gt; 
&gt; This is for your information, and concerns the new EDH MARS document for 2012, and the competency model. I think all of you were invited to follow a training to learn about it, and I can only encourage you to go.
&gt; 
&gt; Another mail follows regarding the same subject.
